content.text:
Welcome!
In this experiment, you will see sets of words, like this:

window-piano

tap here to continue...

Sometimes they will be real words, sometimes not.

Somtimes there will be one real word
and one nonsense word, like this:

window-blargo

tap here to continue...

You will see a happy or sad smiley,
to tell if you got the answer right or not.

tap here to continue...

The experiment takes about 5 minutes.

Try not to make any mistakes,
but don't worry if you do make a few.

We all make mistakes!

tap here to continue...

If one or both of the words is not a real word in English,
like this:

window-blargo

or these:

jupsal-clotrop

tap the red circle

If both words are real words in English, like this:

window-piano

tap the green circle

Ok, practice is over! 

Time for the real experiment.
Remember:
two real words:
one or two nonwords: 

Tap here to begin the experiment...

First, let's try a practice round.

Remember:

two real words
one or two nonsense words

tap here when you are ready to begin...
